## Environment Variables

| Variable | Description | Default |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `OPENCLAW_HOST` | Gateway host | `127.0.0.1` |
| `OPENCLAW_PORT` | Gateway port | `18789` |
| `OPENCLAW_AUTH_TOKEN` | Authentication token | `null` |
| `OPENCLAW_LLM_PROVIDER` | Default LLM provider | - |
| `OPENCLAW_LLM_API_KEY` | LLM API key | - |
| `OPENCLAW_LLM_MODEL` | Default model | `gpt-4` |

